A cyberpunk-style digital illustration depicting a futuristic search interface floating in a neon-drenched void. Multiple translucent holographic cards cascade in a spiral formation, each card displaying abstract geometric patterns and glowing data badges in electric blue, magenta, and cyan. A single luminous card in the foreground pulses brighter than the others, as if selected from the swarm. Thin laser-like connection lines trace between the cards, suggesting relationships and filtering. The background features dark circuit-board patterns with subtle grid lines disappearing into purple-black depths. Small floating hexagonal badges orbit around the central selection, emanating soft neon glows. The atmosphere is moody yet dynamic, with chromatic aberration effects on the edges and subtle digital rain particles falling in the distance.
